extends boolean

snippet dsu "Daily Stand-up" b
`! date +%F`:
	Tomorrow: 🌈
		- TODO
	Grateful: 🙇
		- I’m grateful TODO.
	Loved: ✅
		- TODO
	Loathed: ❌
		- TODO
	Learned: 📘
